definitions.definition: A town in the larger city of Campbelltown, near Sydney , New South Wales .
A local government area in New South Wales , Australia ; in full, the City of Campbelltown .
A suburb of Adelaide in the larger local government area , the City of Campbelltown in South Australia .
Former name of Bluff , New Zealand .
A village in the Potaro-Siparuni region of Guyana .
An unincorporated community in Pike County , Indiana , United States .
An unincorporated community and census-designated place in Lebanon County , Pennsylvania , United States .
